data.description: Looking for the perfect location to call home...look no further! This Inviting 5 Bedroom/3 Bath Pool Home ideally located in the community of Julington Creek Plantation is waiting for you. Features include a spacious kitchen with 42'' cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, smooth-top range w/double ovens, and granite sink. Open family room with gas fireplace and triple sliding doors leads to an amazing pool and outdoor oasis, perfect for entertaining friends and family. An elegant Owners retreat and ensuite including his and her vanities, garden tub and separate frameless glass shower with rain shower head. Upstairs great room and bath with ensuite provides an extra flex space or teen area. Extended 2 car Garage provides plenty of room.
